OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,FA member of the senior leadership team
OL,7,Fat the hospital when Lucy Letby
OL,8,Fcarried out her crimes has been re-
OL,9,Farrested as part of an ongoing
OL,10,Finvestigation into corporate
OL,11,Fmanslaughter and gross negligence
OL,12,Fmanslaughter.
OL,14,FCheshire Police said the arrest came
OL,15,Fafter officers executed a search
OL,16,Fwarrant at a property on 22 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
