OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,FThe individual, who has not been
OL,7,Fidentified but is believed to be one
OL,8,Fof three members of the senior
OL,9,Fleadership team who were arrested in
OL,10,FJune 2025, was detained on suspicion
OL,11,Fof perverting the course of justice.
OL,13,FFormer nurse Letby is serving 15 whole-
OL,14,Flife orders after she was convicted of
OL,15,Fmurdering seven babies and attempting
OL,16,Fto kill seven others - with two
OL,17,Fattempts on one of her victims - at
OL,18,Fthe Countess of Chester Hospital,
OL,19,Fbetween June 2015 and June 2016.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,FFollowing the convictions, in October
OL,7,F2023 Cheshire Police launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation into corporate
OL,9,Fmanslaughter at the hospital, after it
OL,10,Fwas alleged bosses breached their duty
OL,11,Fof care by ignoring signs Letby was
OL,12,Fharming babies on the neonatal ward.
OL,14,FIn a statement about the latest
OL,15,Fupdates in the investigation, the
OL,16,Fforce said: "On Wednesday 22 April
OL,17,Fofficers from Cheshire Constabulary
OL,18,Fexecuted a search warrant at a
OL,19,Fproperty in connection with Operation
OL,20,FDuet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,F"Operation Duet is the ongoing
OL,7,Finvestigation into corporate
OL,8,Fmanslaughter and gross negligence
OL,9,Fmanslaughter at the Countess of
OL,10,FChester Hospital.
OL,12,F"An individual was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of perverting the course of
OL,14,Fjustice. They have subsequently been
OL,15,Fbailed pending further enquiries.
OL,17,F"The searches at the property have now
OL,18,Fconcluded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,F"Both the corporate manslaughter and
OL,7,Fgross negligence manslaughter elements
OL,8,Fof the investigation are continuing
OL,9,Fand there are no set timescales for
OL,10,Fthese."
OL,12,FThe scope of the investigation was
OL,13,Fwidened to include gross negligence
OL,14,Fmanslaughter investigation in March
OL,15,F2025, which is also still ongoing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,FWhile corporate manslaughter is
OL,7,Fdefined by the Crown Prosecution
OL,8,FService as "when a company's gross
OL,9,Fnegligence in managing or organising
OL,10,Fits activities leads to a person's
OL,11,Fdeath", gross negligence manslaughter
OL,12,Fapplies to individuals within the
OL,13,Forganisation and their actions.
OL,15,FPolice are continuing a review of
OL,16,Fdeaths and non-fatal collapses of
OL,17,Fbabies at the neonatal units of the
OL,18,FCountess of Chester and Liverpool
OL,19,FWomen's Hospital during Letby's time
OL,20,Fas a nurse from 2012 to 2016.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1776953470
OL,3,CSenior hospital boss re-arrested as
OL,4,Cpart of Lucy Letby investigation
OL,6,FLetby lost two bids last year to
OL,7,Fchallenge her convictions at the Court
OL,8,Fof Appeal for the seven murders and
OL,9,Fseven attempted murders, and in
OL,10,FOctober for the attempted murder of a
OL,11,Fbaby girl, which she was convicted of
OL,12,Fby a different jury at a retrial.
OL,14,FLady Justice Thirlwall is due to
OL,15,Fpublish the findings from her public
OL,16,Finquiry in 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
